2025-09-10 15:37:04 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:37:04 [INFO] Can continue: Brundt the Chieftain
2025-09-10 15:37:04 [INFO] Can continue: A reduction on sales taxes? Why, I am the only one in<br>the Fremennik who may authorise such a thing. What<br>does an outerlander want with that?
