2025-09-10 15:37:06 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:37:06 [INFO] Can continue: Brundt the Chieftain
2025-09-10 15:37:06 [INFO] Can continue: Hmmm. Interesting. Your trials seem to be very<br>different to those I took as a young lad. Well, I am not<br>adverse in principle to giving a slight tax break to our<br>shops.
2025-09-10 15:37:06 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:37:06 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:37:06 [INFO] Can continue: Brundt the Chieftain
2025-09-10 15:37:06 [INFO] Can continue: There will of course be a shortfall in the tribe's income,<br>that will need to be made up for elsewhere, however.
2025-09-10 15:37:06 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:37:07 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:37:07 [INFO] Can continue: Brundt the Chieftain
2025-09-10 15:37:07 [INFO] Can continue: How about this. For many years Sigli has been the only<br>one in the tribe who knows the locations of the best<br>hunting grounds where game is easiest to catch.
