2025-09-10 15:37:08 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:37:08 [INFO] Can continue: Brundt the Chieftain
2025-09-10 15:37:08 [INFO] Can continue: by lowering sales taxes will be covered. I think this is a<br>more than fair arrangement to make, don't you?
