2025-09-10 15:37:22 [INFO] Can continue: Sigli the Huntsman
2025-09-10 15:37:22 [INFO] Can continue: Well, of course I do. I wouldn't be much of a<br>huntsman if I didn't know where to find my prey now,<br>would I outerlander?
