2025-09-10 15:38:47 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:38:47 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:38:47 [INFO] Can continue: Perhaps I can trade you something for it?
2025-09-10 15:38:47 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:38:48 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:38:48 [INFO] Can continue: Swensen the Navigator
2025-09-10 15:38:48 [INFO] Can continue: A trade? For a map of the best fishing spots in a<br>hundred leagues? I will trade it for no less than a<br>weather forecast from our Seer.
2025-09-10 15:38:48 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:38:49 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:38:49 [INFO] Can continue: Swensen the Navigator
2025-09-10 15:38:49 [INFO] Can continue: As a navigator, the weather is extremely important for<br>plotting the best course. Unfortunately the Seer is<br>always too busy to help me with a forecast.
2025-09-10 15:38:49 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:38:49 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:38:49 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:38:49 [INFO] Can continue: Where could I get a weather forecast from then?
