2025-09-10 15:38:55 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:38:55 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:38:55 [INFO] Can continue: I am trying to become a member of the Fremennik<br>clan! The Chieftain told me that I may be able to gain<br>your vote at the council of elders?
2025-09-10 15:38:55 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:38:55 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:38:55 [INFO] Can continue: Swensen the Navigator
2025-09-10 15:38:55 [INFO] Can continue: You wish to stop being an outerlander? I can<br>understand that! I have no reason why I would prevent<br>you becoming a Fremennik...
2025-09-10 15:38:55 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:38:56 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:38:56 [INFO] Can continue: Swensen the Navigator
2025-09-10 15:38:56 [INFO] Can continue: ...but you must first pass a little test for me to prove<br>you are worthy.
