2025-09-10 15:38:57 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:38:57 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:38:57 [INFO] Can continue: What kind of test?
2025-09-10 15:38:57 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:38:58 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:38:58 [INFO] Can continue: Swensen the Navigator
2025-09-10 15:38:58 [INFO] Can continue: Well, I serve our clan as a navigator. The seas can be<br>a fearful place when you know not where you are<br>heading.
2025-09-10 15:38:58 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:38:59 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:38:59 [INFO] Can continue: Swensen the Navigator
2025-09-10 15:38:59 [INFO] Can continue: Should something happen to me, all members of our<br>tribe have some basic sense of direction so that they<br>may always return safely home.
