2025-09-10 15:38:59 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:38:59 [INFO] Can continue: Swensen the Navigator
2025-09-10 15:38:59 [INFO] Can continue: If you are able to demonstrate to me that you too have<br>a good sense of direction then I will recommend you to<br>the rest of the council of elders immediately.
2025-09-10 15:38:59 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:39:00 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:39:00 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:39:00 [INFO] Can continue: Well, how would I go about showing that?
2025-09-10 15:39:00 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:39:00 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:39:00 [INFO] Can continue: Swensen the Navigator
