2025-09-10 15:39:53 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:39:53 [INFO] Can continue: Can I have a weather forecast then please?
2025-09-10 15:39:53 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:39:54 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:39:54 [INFO] Can continue: Peer the Seer
2025-09-10 15:39:54 [INFO] Can continue: You require a divination of the weather? This is a<br>simple matter for me, but I will require something in<br>return from you for this small service.
2025-09-10 15:39:54 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:39:54 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:39:55 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:39:55 [INFO] Can continue: I knew you were going to say that...
