2025-09-10 15:40:12 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:12 [INFO] ===
2025-09-10 15:40:12 [INFO] Ask about the Merchant's trial
2025-09-10 15:40:12 [INFO] Ask about becoming a Fremennik
2025-09-10 15:40:12 [INFO] ===
2025-09-10 15:40:12 [INFO] 918 Option: Ask about the Merchant's trial
2025-09-10 15:40:14 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:14 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:40:14 [INFO] Can continue: I don't suppose you have any idea where I could find a<br>brave and powerful warrior to act as a bodyguard?
2025-09-10 15:40:14 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:40:15 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:15 [INFO] Can continue: Thorvald the Warrior
2025-09-10 15:40:15 [INFO] Can continue: Know you not who I am outerlander? There are none<br>more brave or powerful than me amongst all the<br>Fremennik!
2025-09-10 15:40:15 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:40:15 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:15 [INFO] Can continue: Thorvald the Warrior
2025-09-10 15:40:15 [INFO] Can continue: However... The role of bodyguard is below me, as a<br>noble warrior. You might as well ask me to babysit the<br>children!
2025-09-10 15:40:15 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:40:16 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:16 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:40:16 [INFO] Can continue: Is there no way you would do this for me?
2025-09-10 15:40:16 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:40:17 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:17 [INFO] Can continue: Thorvald the Warrior
2025-09-10 15:40:17 [INFO] Can continue: There is but one way outerlander. Since I was steeled<br>in battle, I have dreamt of earning my place at the<br>Champions Table in the Long Hall.
2025-09-10 15:40:17 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:40:17 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:17 [INFO] Can continue: Thorvald the Warrior
2025-09-10 15:40:17 [INFO] Can continue: It is a tradition amongst us that the bravest and<br>strongest are honoured with a table of champions to<br>drink and feast all that they can in our Long Hall.
2025-09-10 15:40:17 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:40:18 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:18 [INFO] Can continue: Thorvald the Warrior
2025-09-10 15:40:18 [INFO] Can continue: Unfortunately, there are only a fixed number of places<br>available at the table, and these places were all filled<br>many moons ago by others.
2025-09-10 15:40:18 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:40:18 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:18 [INFO] Can continue: Thorvald the Warrior
2025-09-10 15:40:18 [INFO] Can continue: Although my worthiness is undeniable, the only way I<br>may take my place is if one of those already there die,<br>or give up their place to me voluntarily.
2025-09-10 15:40:18 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:40:19 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:19 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:40:19 [INFO] Can continue: So you want me to go kill one of them off for you?<br>Make it look like an accident?
2025-09-10 15:40:19 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:40:20 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:20 [INFO] Can continue: Thorvald the Warrior
2025-09-10 15:40:20 [INFO] Can continue: WHAT? No, no, not at all! I am shocked you would<br>suggest such a thing!
2025-09-10 15:40:20 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:40:21 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:21 [INFO] Can continue: Thorvald the Warrior
2025-09-10 15:40:21 [INFO] Can continue: If you can persuade one of the Revellers to give up<br>their Champions' Token to you so that I might take<br>their place, you may have my contract as a bodyguard.
2025-09-10 15:40:21 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:40:22 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:22 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:40:22 [INFO] Can continue: Okay, I'll see what I can do.
