2025-09-10 15:40:49 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:49 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:40:49 [INFO] Can continue: I don't suppose you have any idea where I could find a<br>token to allow a seat at the champions table, do you?
