2025-09-10 15:40:50 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:50 [INFO] Can continue: Manni the Reveller
2025-09-10 15:40:50 [INFO] Can continue: As a matter of fact, I do. I have one right here. I<br>earnt my place here at the longhall for surviving over<br>5000 battles and raiding parties.
