2025-09-10 15:40:51 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:51 [INFO] Can continue: Manni the Reveller
2025-09-10 15:40:51 [INFO] Can continue: Due to my contribution to the tribe, I am now<br>permitted to spend my days here in the longhall<br>listening to the epic tales of the bard, and drinking beer.
2025-09-10 15:40:51 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:40:52 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:52 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:40:52 [INFO] Can continue: Cool. That sounds pretty sweet! So I guess you don't<br>want to give it away?
2025-09-10 15:40:52 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:40:52 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:52 [INFO] Can continue: Manni the Reveller
2025-09-10 15:40:52 [INFO] Can continue: I think it sounds better than it actually is outerlander.<br>I miss my glory days of combat on the battlefield. And<br>to tell you the truth, the beer here isn't great, and the<br>bards' music is lousy.
2025-09-10 15:40:52 [INFO] Continue
