2025-09-10 15:40:53 [INFO] Can continue: Manni the Reveller
2025-09-10 15:40:53 [INFO] Can continue: I would happily give up my token if it were not for the<br>one thing that keeps me here. Our barkeep is one of<br>the best in the world, and has worked in taverns across<br>the land.
2025-09-10 15:40:53 [INFO] Continue
