2025-09-10 15:40:54 [INFO] Can continue: Manni the Reveller
2025-09-10 15:40:54 [INFO] Can continue: When she was younger, she experimented a lot with her<br>drinks, and invented a cocktail so alcoholic and tasty<br>that it has become something of a legend to all who<br>enjoy a drink.
