2025-09-10 15:40:55 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:55 [INFO] Can continue: Manni the Reveller
2025-09-10 15:40:55 [INFO] Can continue: Unfortunately, she decided that cocktails were not a<br>suitable drink for Fremennik warriors, and vowed to<br>never again make it.
