2025-09-10 15:40:55 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:40:55 [INFO] Can continue: Manni the Reveller
2025-09-10 15:40:55 [INFO] Can continue: I have been here every day since she returned, hoping<br>that someday she might change her mind and I might<br>try this legendary cocktail for myself. Alas, it has never<br>come to pass...
