2025-09-10 15:48:19 [INFO] Can continue: Thorvald the Warrior
2025-09-10 15:48:19 [INFO] Can continue: Hahahahaha! You certainly show some spirit for an<br>outerlander!
2025-09-10 15:48:19 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:48:20 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:48:20 [INFO] Can continue: Thorvald the Warrior
2025-09-10 15:48:20 [INFO] Can continue: But spirit does not always make a good warrior. It<br>takes both skill and spirit to be so. I have a test that I<br>give all Fremenniks on their path to be a member of the<br>clan.
2025-09-10 15:48:20 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:48:20 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:48:20 [INFO] Can continue: Thorvald the Warrior
2025-09-10 15:48:20 [INFO] Can continue: My test will challenge both your combat prowess and<br>your bravery equally. Should you pass it you will earn<br>my vote at the council, and more importantly my<br>respect for you as a warrior.
2025-09-10 15:48:20 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:48:22 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:48:22 [INFO] Can continue: Thorvald the Warrior
2025-09-10 15:48:22 [INFO] Can continue: So what say you, outerlander? Are you prepared for<br>the battle?
2025-09-10 15:48:22 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:48:23 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:48:23 [INFO] ===
2025-09-10 15:48:23 [INFO] Yes
2025-09-10 15:48:23 [INFO] No
2025-09-10 15:48:23 [INFO] ===
2025-09-10 15:48:23 [INFO] 918 Option: 1 Yes
2025-09-10 15:48:25 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:48:25 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 15:48:25 [INFO] Can continue: Am I prepared? I'll show you what combat's all about,<br>you big sissy barbarian type guy!
2025-09-10 15:48:25 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:48:26 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:48:26 [INFO] Can continue: Thorvald the Warrior
2025-09-10 15:48:26 [INFO] Can continue: Hahahahaha! I'm beginning to like you already,<br>outerlander!
2025-09-10 15:48:26 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:48:26 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:48:26 [INFO] Can continue: Thorvald the Warrior
2025-09-10 15:48:26 [INFO] Can continue: Then allow me to present you with my challenge; This<br>ladder here will take you to a place of combat. I have<br>placed a special warrior down there to challenge you.
2025-09-10 15:48:26 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:48:27 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:48:27 [INFO] Can continue: Thorvald the Warrior
2025-09-10 15:48:27 [INFO] Can continue: Battle him to the death, and you will pass my challenge.<br>If at any point you wish to leave combat, simply climb<br>back up the ladder, to leave that place.
2025-09-10 15:48:27 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:48:28 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:48:28 [INFO] Can continue: Thorvald the Warrior
2025-09-10 15:48:28 [INFO] Can continue: If you leave you will of course fail the test. You may<br>retry my test in the future if you fail, but you must<br>stay down there until the death if you wish for my vote<br>at the council.
2025-09-10 15:48:28 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 15:48:28 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 15:48:28 [INFO] Can continue: Thorvald the Warrior
2025-09-10 15:48:28 [INFO] Can continue: You must defeat him three times to prove that you are<br>worthy. The fourth time that you fight him will be to<br>the death, so do not show cowardice.
2025-09-10 15:48:28 [INFO] Continue
