2025-09-10 16:04:40 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:04:40 [INFO] Can continue: Peer the Seer
2025-09-10 16:04:40 [INFO] Can continue: Hello outerlander. What do you want?
2025-09-10 16:04:40 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:04:41 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:04:41 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 16:04:41 [INFO] Can continue: Hello. I'm looking for members of the council of elders<br>to vote for me to become a Fremennik.
2025-09-10 16:04:41 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:04:41 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:04:41 [INFO] Can continue: Peer the Seer
2025-09-10 16:04:41 [INFO] Can continue: Are you now? Well that is interesting. Usually<br>outerlanders do not concern themselves with our ways<br>like that.
2025-09-10 16:04:41 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:04:42 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:04:42 [INFO] Can continue: Peer the Seer
2025-09-10 16:04:42 [INFO] Can continue: I am one of the members of the council of elders, and<br>should you be able to prove to me that you have<br>something to offer my clan
2025-09-10 16:04:42 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:04:43 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:04:43 [INFO] Can continue: Peer the Seer
2025-09-10 16:04:43 [INFO] Can continue: I will vote in your favour at the next meeting.
2025-09-10 16:04:43 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:04:44 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:04:44 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 16:04:44 [INFO] Can continue: How can I prove that to you?
2025-09-10 16:04:44 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:04:44 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:04:44 [INFO] Can continue: Peer the Seer
2025-09-10 16:04:44 [INFO] Can continue: Well, I have but a simple test. This building behind me<br>is my house. Inside I have constructed a puzzle.
2025-09-10 16:04:44 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:04:46 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:04:46 [INFO] Can continue: Peer the Seer
2025-09-10 16:04:46 [INFO] Can continue: As a Seer to the clan, I value intelligence very highly,<br>so you may think of it as an intelligence test of sorts.
2025-09-10 16:04:46 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:04:46 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:04:46 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 16:04:46 [INFO] Can continue: An intelligence test? I thought barbarians were stupid!
2025-09-10 16:04:46 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:04:47 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:04:47 [INFO] Can continue: Peer the Seer
2025-09-10 16:04:47 [INFO] Can continue: That is the opinion that outerlanders usually hold of my<br>people, it is true. But that is because people often<br>confuse knowledge with wisdom.
2025-09-10 16:04:47 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 16:04:48 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 16:04:48 [INFO] Can continue: Peer the Seer
2025-09-10 16:04:48 [INFO] Can continue: My puzzle tests not what you know, but what you can<br>work out. All members of our clan have been tested<br>when they took their trials.
2025-09-10 16:04:48 [INFO] Continue
