2025-09-10 17:57:33 [INFO] Can continue: Niloof
2025-09-10 17:57:33 [INFO] Can continue: Back away! Back away! Wait... you're human!
2025-09-10 17:57:33 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 17:57:34 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 17:57:34 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 17:57:34 [INFO] Can continue: That's right, I'm on a quest for King Lathas. I need to<br>find a way through these caverns.
2025-09-10 17:57:34 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 17:57:35 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 17:57:35 [INFO] Can continue: Niloof
2025-09-10 17:57:35 [INFO] Can continue: Well good luck with that. We came here as miners,<br>completely unaware of the evil that lurked here. There's<br>no way through, not while Iban still rules. He controls<br>the gateway, the only way to the other side.
2025-09-10 17:57:35 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 17:57:36 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 17:57:36 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 17:57:36 [INFO] Can continue: What gateway?
2025-09-10 17:57:36 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 17:57:37 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 17:57:37 [INFO] Can continue: Niloof
2025-09-10 17:57:37 [INFO] Can continue: The Well of Voyage. It acts as a portal through the last<br>section of the caverns. It's the only way into the west.<br>Iban has corrupted it though. Now he uses it to dispose<br>of those who displease him.
2025-09-10 17:57:37 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 17:57:37 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 17:57:37 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-10 17:57:37 [INFO] Can continue: Well I'll just have to kill him then.
2025-09-10 17:57:37 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 17:57:38 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 17:57:38 [INFO] Can continue: Niloof
2025-09-10 17:57:38 [INFO] Can continue: Ha! Good luck with that. If we knew how, we'd have<br>slain him already.
2025-09-10 17:57:38 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 17:57:38 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 17:57:38 [INFO] Can continue: Niloof
2025-09-10 17:57:38 [INFO] Can continue: Seek out the witch, his guide, his only confidante. Only<br>she knows how to rid us of Iban.
2025-09-10 17:57:38 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-10 17:57:39 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 17:57:39 [INFO] Can continue: Niloof
2025-09-10 17:57:39 [INFO] Can continue: She lives on the platforms above, we dare not go there.<br>Here, take some food to aid your journey.
