2025-09-10 17:57:55 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 17:57:55 [INFO] Can continue: Klank
2025-09-10 17:57:55 [INFO] Can continue: They were normal once, adventurers, treasure hunters.<br>But men are weak, they couldn't ignore the voices.
