2025-09-10 17:57:55 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-10 17:57:55 [INFO] Can continue: Klank
2025-09-10 17:57:55 [INFO] Can continue: Now they all seem to think with one conscience... As if<br>they're being controlled by one being...
