2025-09-10 17:57:56 [INFO] Can continue: Klank
2025-09-10 17:57:56 [INFO] Can continue: Maybe... maybe Zamorak himself. Those who try and<br>fight it are locked in cages, until their minds are too<br>weak to resist.
