2025-09-11 08:12:26 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-11 08:12:26 [INFO] Can continue: Charlie
2025-09-11 08:12:26 [INFO] Can continue: A few weeks ago we had a delivery of a northern<br>ferret. They're funny little creatures. Turns out<br>they're tricksy little blighters too.
